@against_right_and_left
title: Against Right and Left
subtitle: As a Centrist, Hilferding seeks to steer a course between the party's factions.
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
choose-if: advisor_action_timer = 0
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 5; advisor_action_time = time; center_strength += 10; left_strength -= 5; labor_strength -= 5; neorevisionist_strength -= 5; center_dissent -= 10

We have reduced the strength of the dissident factions in the party.

@agriculture
title: Agricultural Policy
subtitle: Baade is the Minister of Agriculture.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0 and spd_in_government and agriculture_minister_party == "SPD"
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?][? if not spd_in_government : The <span style="color: #c00000;">SPD</span> is not in government. ?][? if agriculture_minister_party != "SPD": The <span style="color: #c00000;">SPD</span> does not have the Agriculture Ministry. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; agricultural_policy_timer -= 6; last_advisor_action = 1
go-to: agricultural_policy

@finance_ministry_
title: Fiscal Policy
subtitle: As Finance Minister, Hilferding can enact tax policies.
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?] [? if spd_in_government = 0 : <span style="color: #c00000;">SPD</span> not in government: ?] [? if finance_minister_party != "SPD" : The <span style="color: #c00000;">SPD</span> does not control the finance ministry. ?]
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0 and spd_in_government == 1 and finance_minister_party == "SPD"
